## Code

### sync-journal.ps1

Opens Claude in your browser with a reminder prompt to trigger a journal sync.

```powershell
# Journal Sync — opens your Claude chat to sync your journal
$url = "https://claude.ai/chat/new"
Start-Process $url
Write-Host ""
Write-Host "Opening Claude..." -ForegroundColor Cyan
Write-Host ""
Write-Host "Just type:  sync my journal" -ForegroundColor Yellow
Write-Host ""
Write-Host "Then download the file Claude sends and click 'Yes' to overwrite." -ForegroundColor Gray
Write-Host ""
Start-Sleep -Seconds 3
```

